1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,625
Take a moment to check in inside.

2
00:00:01,625 --> 00:00:03,947
Ask: What part of me is most present
right now?

3
00:00:09,947 --> 00:00:09,947
<break time="3s" />

4
00:00:09,947 --> 00:00:11,433
Notice the first thing that comes.

5
00:00:11,433 --> 00:00:14,962
It might be a thought, a feeling, a body
sensation, or an impulse.

6
00:00:14,962 --> 00:00:17,841
Now ask: What is this part trying to help
me with?

7
00:00:23,841 --> 00:00:23,841
<break time="3s" />

8
00:00:23,841 --> 00:00:24,630
Listen gently.

9
00:00:24,630 --> 00:00:28,717
Now ask: What does this part need from me
in the next few minutes?

10
00:00:34,717 --> 00:00:34,717
<break time="3s" />

11
00:00:34,717 --> 00:00:39,407
Maybe space, reassurance, a boundary,
rest, a breath, or a small action.

12
00:00:39,407 --> 00:00:43,353
Say to the part: I see that you are here.
I want to understand. You do not have to

13
00:00:43,353 --> 00:00:44,376
take over completely.

14
00:00:44,376 --> 00:00:45,723
Take one slow breath.

15
00:00:48,723 --> 00:00:51,463
And carry this awareness into what comes
next.

